*bsnes-0.069 (25 Sep 2010)

  25 Sep 2010; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> +bsnes-0.069.ebuild,
  +files/bsnes-0.069-makefile.patch:
  Bumped.

*bsnes-0.068 (21 Aug 2010)

  21 Aug 2010; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> -bsnes-0.067.ebuild,
  +bsnes-0.068.ebuild, +files/bsnes-0.068-makefile.patch:
  Bumped. This version adds selectable cpu cores and a launcher. The ebuild
  compiles all of them, so build times will be longer than in previous
  versions.

