*bsnes-0.063_p10 (08 Apr 2010)

  08 Apr 2010; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> +bsnes-0.063_p10.ebuild,
  +files/bsnes-0.063_p10-makefile.patch:
  Added technical preview with cycle-based PPU. Not meant for mere mortals.
  Also, no snesreader, snesfilter and sgb bundled with this release. Use
  this only if you know what you're doing.

