*bsnes-0.059_p2 (14 Jan 2010)

  14 Jan 2010; Michał Ziąbkowski <mziab@o2.pl> +bsnes-0.059_p2.ebuild:
  Added latest development snapshot. Since those are packaged with extra
  libraries, the ebuild blocks on external copies of snesreader, snesfilter
  and supergameboy, and builds the bundled ones. To my mind, that's the best
  solution.

